### REST API Implementation

#### INSERT CATEGORY => tindapress/v1/category/insert

REQUEST: 
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=snky (value=session key), key=wpid (value=wordpress id), key=title (value= title of category), key=info (value= information of category), key = types (store or product)

RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Plugin Missing!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Verification Issues!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Category must be product or store only' data: null
- code: 'error' message: 'An error occured while submitting data to database' data: null


IF SUCCESS:
```
    {
        "status": "success",
        "message": "Data has been added successfully!"
    }
```

#### UPDATE CATEGORY by CATEGORY `ID` => tindapress/v1/category/update

REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=snky (value=session key), key=wpid (value=wordpress id), key=title (value= title of category), key=info (value= information of category),  key = types (types of category), key = catid (Category iD)
RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Plugin Missing!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Verification Issues!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Category must be product or store only' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'This category does not exists' data: null


IF SUCCESS:
```
    {
        "status": "success",
        "message": "Data has been updated successfully!"
    }
```

#### DELETE CATEGORY by CATEGORY `ID` => => tindapress/v1/category/delete
 
REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=snky (value=session key), key=wpid (value=wordpress id), key = catid (Category iD)
RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Plugin Missing!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Verification Issues!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Category not found' data: null

IF SUCCESS:
```
    {
        "status": "success",
        "message": "Data has been deleted successfully!"
    }
```

#### LIST of CATEGORIES => tindapress/v1/category/list/all

REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=snky (value=session key), key=wpid (value=wordpress id)
RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Plugin Missing!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Verification Issues!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'No results found' data: null


IF SUCCESS:
```
  {
    "status": "success",
    "data": [
        {
            "ID": "3",
            "types": "product",
            "title": "Chicken Meals",
            "info": "Category food product"
        },
        {
            "ID": "6",
            "types": "product",
            "title": "Happy Meal",
            "info": "Happy na, Meal pa."
        },
        {
            "ID": "7",
            "types": "product",
            "title": "Classic Pizzas",
            "info": "Not special pizza."
        },
        {
            "ID": "8",
            "types": "product",
            "title": "Overloaded Pizzas",
            "info": "Pizza with meat, cheese, bacon, etc."
        }
    ]
}
```

#### LIST CATEGORIES by `STORE` or `PRODUCT` => => tindapress/v1/category/list/type

REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=snky (value=session key), key=wpid (value=wordpress id), key = type (value= store or product)
RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Plugin Missing!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Verification Issues!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Category must be product or store only' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'No results found' data: null


IF SUCCESS:
```
  {
    "status": "success",
    "data": [
        {
            "ID": "3",
            "title": "Chicken Meals",
            "info": "Category food product"
        },
        {
            "ID": "6",
            "title": "Happy Meal",
            "info": "Happy na, Meal pa."
        }
}
```

#### SELECT CATEGORY by `ID` => tindapress/v1/category/select

REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=snky (value=session key), key=wpid (value=wordpress id), key = type (value= store or product), key = catid (value= category id) 
RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Plugin Missing!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Verification Issues!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'No results found' data: null


IF SUCCESS:
```
  {
    "status": "success",
    "data": [
        {
            "ID": "16",
            "types": "product",
            "title": "Milktea",
            "info": "A combination of milk and tea",
            "status": "1"
        }
}
```

#### SELECT CATEGORY by `STORE ID` => tindapress/v1/category/select/store

REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=snky (value=session key), key=wpid (value=wordpress id), key = type (value= store or product), key = stid (value= category id) 
RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Plugin Missing!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Verification Issues!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'No results found' data: null


IF SUCCESS:
```
  {
    "status": "success",
    "data": [
        {
            "ID": "16",
            "types": "product",
            "title": "Milktea",
            "info": "A combination of milk, tea, and sugar"
        }
}
```

#### INSERT CATEGORY within the STORE => tindapress/v1/category/store/insert

REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=snky (value=session key), key=wpid (value=wordpress id), key=title (value= title of category), key=info (value= information of category), key = stid (store id)

RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Plugin Missing!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Verification Issues!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'This store does not exists' data: null
- code: 'error' message: 'An error occured while submitting data to database' data: null


IF SUCCESS:
```
    {
        "status": "success",
        "message": "Data has been added successfully!"
    }
```